    "The study evaluates the model on the ARM Cortex-A53 processor.",
    "Results show that the DNN-based approach provides early WCET estimates that, while not precise enough to serve as strict upper bounds, offer valuable insights during early system design.",
    "This helps prevent overestimation, which can lead to costly overqualified systems, and underestimation, which risks financial loss due to system underperformance.Moghaddam and Parand [94] introduce a method for WCET estimation using Support Vector Machine Regression (SVR) with Legendre orthogonal kernel functions.",
    "The complexity of software and hardware makes WCET estimation challenging.",
    "This method employs ML to enhance accuracy by leveraging the minimal data redundancy in orthogonal functions."
